trans-unit.source: Defines the template of the final step for creating a user account with the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard"></xref> control.
The CompleteWizardStep class is derived from <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TemplatedWizardStep> and used by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard> control.
By default the CompleteWizardStep step is displayed after the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizardStep> step.
The CompleteWizardStep step is a required step of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard> control.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep"></xref> class.

Gets or sets the type of user interface (UI) to display for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep"></xref> page of a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard"></xref> control.

The StepType property specifies the type of navigation UI to display for the final user account creation step (the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizardStep> step) of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard> control.

> [!CAUTION] > The StepType property overrides the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepBase.StepType%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property to ensure that <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep> is always set to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepType> value of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepType> enumeration.
Attempting to set the StepType property to a different value will result in an <xref:System.InvalidOperationException>.
This property cannot be set by themes or style sheet themes.
For more information, see <xref:System.Web.UI.ThemeableAttribute> and [ASP.NET Themes and Skins](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
The <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepType"></xref> enumeration value for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepType"></xref> enumeration.
An attempt was made to set the StepType property.
Gets or sets the title to display for the final user account creation step of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard"></xref> control.
The value of this property, when set, can be saved automatically to a resource file by using a designer tool.
For more information, see <xref:System.ComponentModel.LocalizableAttribute> and [Globalization and Localization](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
The title to use for the final user account creation step of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard"></xref> control.
